{"tid":884312,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"傳支那阻街垃圾 ofo 負債64.96億元冥幣，準備破產重組方案","createTime":"2018-10-31T13:21:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-06T14:28:37.000Z","uid":79563,"like":31,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"163b47a0be274cd0889c5fe08ee750f83a21209b","tid":884312,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T13:21:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20181031/bkn-20181031161725406-1031_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20181031%2Fbkn-20181031161725406-1031_00842_001.html&d=6KMsGPFjoDfG8qlkfqB40%2FiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=fb16fad8\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20181031/bkn-20181031161725406-1031_00842_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://macautimes.cc/Upfile/upload02(198).jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmacautimes.cc%2FUpfile%2Fupload02%28198%29.jpg&h=bd4a84fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n支媒引述消息報道，支那共享單車巨頭ofo小黃車開始準備破產重組方案，已有一家大型券商中介機構參與。<br />\n<br />\n報道引述一份約半年前ofo的負債表，公司整體負債64.96億元冥幣(下同)，其中，用戶押金36.5億元，供應鏈為10.2億元。"},{"pid":"b4adf2da6856401a26771b2a9d8b0f1c78539a02","tid":884312,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T13:23:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2018/10/28/ofo/life-tech/bike/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2018%2F10%2F28%2Fofo%2Flife-tech%2Fbike%2F&d=6KMsGPFjoDfG8qlkfqB40%2FiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=3373f8a9\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2018/10/28/ofo/life-tech/bike/</a><br />\n<br />\n共享單車「小黃車 ofo」被指拖延退還按金　3日變15日網民齊喊「退錢！」<br />\n<br />\n根據大陸媒體報道，有網民反映共享單車公司小黃車 ofo 的按金退還周期不斷延長。原本退還按金只需要 3 個工作天，但愈拖愈久，現在已變成了需要最多 15 個工作天時間處理。有網民聲稱申請一個月後仍未收到按金退款。<br />\n<br />\n現時不少共享單車公司都面對經營困難，就算似乎聲稱市場佔有率第一的小黃車 ofo 仍難免受影響。根據大陸媒體《中新經緯》報道，有網民反映小黃車 ofo 的退還按金所需時間不斷延長，最初只需 3 個工作天就能退還按金，其後變成了 1－10 個工作天，而現在已變成了 1－15 個工作天才能退款。<br />\n<br />\n大陸媒體《中新經緯》曾致電客戶服務熱線，但該熱線長期處於無人接聽的狀態。有網民指在申請退款後 1 個月仍未收到，打客戶服務熱線卻被指「此號碼不存在」。有網民指按金已被退還，但其支付寶賬戶卻遲遲未到賬。不少網民都要求小黃車 ofo「快點退錢」。<br />\n<br />\n《中新經緯》引述當地律師表示，共享單車等電子商務經營者將所收按金、預付費挪作他用，是嚴重損害消費者權益行為，其行為已經涉嫌欺詐。<br />\n<br />\n資料來源：中新經緯 via 中國新聞網"},{"pid":"f2ea5419f19131fe243b43adc13e254680839783","tid":884312,"uid":141151,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T13:26:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22b5c6b101220f1fe6f21d7cf31fcd36e7de82d6","tid":884312,"uid":37375,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T13:26:39.000Z","msg":"新四大發明wo"},{"pid":"0f3b3c4d21eaab5d667a8ae249828993ec8f2d49","tid":884312,"uid":52946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T13:28:13.000Z","msg":"正宗偷呃鬼騙"},{"pid":"b9e5b3deae9afbad18eaac36df9faabe743c5d4e","tid":884312,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"22b5c6b101220f1fe6f21d7cf31fcd36e7de82d6","tid":884312,"uid":37375,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T13:26:39.000Z","msg":"新四大發明wo"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T13:31:31.000Z","msg":"sabotage 發明<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"031218c1421de749a73403adbe162849a29759aa","tid":884312,"uid":177047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T13:35:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f4056d7eb00e15ac3610237741619166b9ed42b","tid":884312,"uid":12021,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T13:38:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c751a806120882958095353c75e5e9da00ea3c0f","tid":884312,"uid":60120,"like":