src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n世界第一"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T13:51:37.000Z","msg":"其實大陸生意全部都係搭雞棚引人投資再走佬"},{"pid":"0b86648e72e7bb264a71e8770609a0b8e2e685b5","tid":884312,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T14:42:08.000Z","msg":"一架單車成本幾錢?"},{"pid":"dd7115a93e824618b0a2e6a26249408c1ae617a0","tid":884312,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T17:44:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82c635c40a11cb06f20133e2662bc964160eaa68","tid":884312,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T17:46:07.000Z","msg":"【最賤港豬用OFO】5創辦人全為共產黨 修改公司章程訂明黨組織法定實質領導地位<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180930/large/1538307516_17c0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180930%2Flarge%2F1538307516_17c0.jpg&h=baacacd8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n支那加強黨建，更要由國企，擴展至一眾民企、特別是互聯網企業。支那共享單車的巨頭ofo，更比同行走前一步，在今年6月已提出，將會通過召開股東大會，修改公司章程，明確訂明黨組織法定的實質領導地位，或成內地互聯網企業首例。<br />\n<br />\n身兼公司創辦人的黨委總書記書戴威解釋，將黨領導核心寫入章程，是為了深入貫徹中共十九大的精神的重要舉措，是非國有企業黨建的「創新」。<br />\n<br />\n按照官媒的報道，即使黨委的領導尚未寫入公司章程，黨委領導已滲入公司決策，例如重要人事任免、涉及公共利益的重大事項決策，由黨委會討論，醞釀成熟後才進入公司經營層面。<br />\nofo目前尚未上市，股東以其他龍頭科網公司、以及國內的私募基金為主，例如是滴滴出行、阿里巴巴、螞蟻金服、弘毅投資等，可想而知，將黨委寫入公司章程的決定，大有可能獲股東大會通過。<br />\n<br />\n創辦人屬官二代<br />\n<br />\n作為創新民企的ofo，在黨建工作行得最前，多少與幾名創辦人背景有關。ofo 5名創辦人都是在學期間入黨，其中兩人早在高中階段入黨，另外三人在大學階段入黨。<br />\n<br />\nofo在成立早期已經設黨小組，2017年7月正式成立黨委，5名創辦人全部成為公司黨委，由創辦人、首席執行官戴威親自出任黨委總書記，在同行中相當少見。<br />\n<br />\n新華社今年4月報道指出，有人勸戴威不要出任黨委書記，以免影響海外市場開拓，但他本人認為，新時代青年黨員要堅定「四個自信（中國特色社會主義道路自信、理論自信、制度自信、文化自信）」，要「亮明」身份。戴威本人其實是官二代，1991年出生於安徽宣城高幹家庭，父親長期在鐵路系統工程，曾任支那中鐵黨委書記、總裁，現任國資委直接管理的中國化學工程集團黨委書記、董事長。"},{"pid":"fcf078c7d8871ab7d7c615b5754ce19624ed47e5","tid":884312,"uid":36901,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T18:04:24.000Z","msg":"執還執<br />\n唔該清埋的垃圾先好執"},{"pid":"765e506d8b2a7749f1cd28e0822e6c6102607a18","tid":884312,"uid":61280,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T18:35:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>租單車做到負債64億<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n世界第一</blockquote><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">乜都假，至緊要嬴！！！！</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e44d69f03d294b25dc0e2fbe787055a0ccdda40e","tid":884312,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T18:40:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又多間"},{"pid":"5e2a52d49b0d84d0f3a99d1aa9777f619be74c21","tid":884312,"uid":219590,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T21:50:31.000Z","msg":"每次見到支那破產，爆炸，死人新聞都好興奮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a02a269b8c9491168dc0035f02fbf094f8e58bec","tid":884312,"uid":109780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T23:56:00.000Z","msg":"差少少就係64.89億<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cfd293a0d2b07eb99ecbee57d82cd978ff40746","tid":884312,"uid":186087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T23:59:15.000Z","msg":"騙局。腦細攞夠融資走佬"},{"pid":"dd004d131ef369ba13f3c7492b3c88f0db845061","tid":884312,"uid":28195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T00:26:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nkaPDRJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnkaPDRJ.png&h=3ebeeede&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k60oJiq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk60oJiq.png&h=82fd5f92&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4327ddee8c0c53eb4d029620a1cab988bf7f23ce","tid":884312,"uid":39365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T00:46:08.000Z","msg":"OFO好似後期已經跟阿里定騰信結盟, 唔收按金就可以用, 我當時都諗緊佢D資金點搵返黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0113ae0a2c53929f3809687d3795348d2734ce1e","tid":884312,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T00:52:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ec226d8234044229931d189029816ffe5a04759","tid":884312,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T01:09:44.000Z","msg":"cap完水走人"},{"pid":"bf95d241748633a1609c35d3db333f1487c9bf8e","tid":884312,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T05:52:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}